{
  "stem": "10353.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And at the time-- at that time, he told me that they were herded into a ghetto, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he told me the approximate place where he is.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he says, I don't know where your mother is.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They were separated.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He didn't tell me but I found out later that my other sister, the one that was originally arrested because of the false documentation, was eventually released, And she went into hiding.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The only thing, he wrote me this letter, and he told me that they don't live anymore at home.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They are all in a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he only wrote me Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He said, [SPEAKING YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I don't know whether you understand [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Yiddish ?].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He says, 'Your brother, Israel'-- which [INAUDIBLE] you might remember-- 'needs great healing.' [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And that was the last time I heard.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[CRYING] [PAUSES FOR 10 SECONDS] My other sister, that I told you that was in Cluj, that was arrested, she was eventually put in a-- in-- into a camp for aliens.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And in-- in 1944, that was in May-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] towards the end of May, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the way I know it, they were-- they were deported to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The entire city of Satu Mare was deported.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We didn't know at that time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We didn't know where they were deported.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "The rumor was that they were resettled.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I mean, that was the official-- the official version, that they were resettled.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And they are apparently, they are being given some very nice place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But we later, of course, found out that they were deported to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] As for myself, I was in the work brigade, and--",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
